txt.en: 'Would you look at this. I'm helping you complete Mines of Moria content now too! I'm a multi- purpose cat, I am. Oh, and look at this, I have a bunch of Item Advancement stuff to give you. That's so cool.\n\n'Alrighty, let's do this, eh?'
'Book I of the Mines of Moria coming right up! Enjoy!'
Level Up: Mines of Moria - Book I
Completion of this quest will flag your character has having completed all the quests in Book I of the Mines of Moria Epic quest series.
